{"tid":237458,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"Google 新系統 Fuchsia OS 曝光, 或將取代 Android (附體驗 Apk)","createTime":"2017-05-10T11:36:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-11T07:20:38.000Z","uid":27240,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0f8b32a94f07e9fc19f124136093b345cd8c1c33","tid":237458,"uid":27240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T11:36:26.000Z","msg":"Android 系統建基於 Linux 為核心的系統 , 但其需通過核心模擬運行 , 這成了 Android 系統發展最大的致命傷 , 更令應用程式不可以直接的運行 , 成了與 iOS 最大的效果差距 . 開發者都認為 , 如果需要改變這情況 , Android 就需要「砍掉重練」.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://qooah.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/18424612_10154599792273450_192687867_n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fqooah.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F05%2F18424612_10154599792273450_192687867_n.jpg&h=6fa2af48&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n要「砍掉重練」是需要多大的勇氣 ? 估計不是每間公司都有這勇氣 , 但 Google 從來都是一家邊試邊走的公司 . 早前傳出 Google 將開發一個新的系統 Fuchsia OS , 傳聞這個新系統或將取代 Android 及 Chrome OS .<br />\n<br />\nFuchsia OS 早前只是傳聞 , 但近日這個傳聞已經呈現在大家眼前 , 因為 Fuchsia OS 的介面已經曝光 , 開發者發現一款稱作「Armadillo」的 Fuchsia UI , 而且被抽出製成了 APK 可以下載 .<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://qooah.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/fuchsia235.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fqooah.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F05%2Ffuchsia235.jpg&h=750fac49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nFuchsia OS 是一款多平台的新系統 , 可以同時使用在手機、平板、PC 等多個平台之上 , Fuchsia OS 絕對是「砍掉重練」的新作 , 有別於現時的 Android 及 Chrome OS , 它們都是以 Linux 為基礎 , 但 Fuchsia OS 則捨棄了 Linux 核心 , 改以更輕量化的「Magenta」內核 , 可以支援 ARM 及 64bit Intel X86 架構. 它同時是以 Google 的一組跨平台 SDK「Flutter」及 Google 自家的 Dart 語言來開發完成 , Dart 語言好處是完全的可以跨平台 , 這語言不管是 iOS 還是 Android 都可以運行 .<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">Armadillo Fuchsia UI 初體驗</span></span><br />\n<br />\nArmadillo 的初體驗 APK 已經可以下載及安裝 , 於測試中筆者發現其介面方式與 Android 十分之不同 . 大體分成 3個部份 .<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://qooah.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/18406427_10154599779358450_932185820_o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fqooah.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F05%2F18406427_10154599779358450_932185820_o.jpg&h=ee637739&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n上段為「Story Card」的 App 區, 用來分放 Apps , 當長按這些「Story Card」是可以任意移動及重疊 , 以成為幾個 App 同時使用的畫面 .<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://qooah.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/18426007_10154599779048450_154268019_n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fqooah.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F05%2F18426007_10154599779048450_154268019_n.jpg&h=5f55eb91&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中段就是自己的人像、時間、位置 , 再點入去就是快速設定中心等 .<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://qooah.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/18425604_10154599778658450_668607276_n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fqooah.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F05%2F18425604_10154599778658450_668607276_n.jpg&h=1cb3e4cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n下段就是就像是 Google Now、及通知中心等排佈 .<br />\n<br />\n目前看來 , Google 是否真的會用 Fuchsia OS 取代 Android 或 Chrome OS 言之過早 . 起碼在初步的介面體驗看來不論操作友善度還是實用性都無法與 Android 或 Chrome OS 相比 . 加上 Android 坐擁超過 80% 市佔的今日 , 根本不需急於改換新系統 . 或者一切在本月的 Google I/O 會有更多資料 .<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n Armadillo 的初體驗 APK下載<a href=\"http://download.qooah.com/files/google-fuchsia-os\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fdownload.qooah.com%2Ffiles%2Fgoogle-fuchsia-os&d=PT6dGXJ5JuBAxmbDRmxpcDM0pwszV1jUpWwTgNsMWwc%3D&h=027f0fc0\" target=\"_blank\">http://download.qooah.com/files/google-fuchsia-os</a><br />\n<br />\n原文 <a href=\"http://Qooah.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FQooah.com&d=PT6dGXJ5JuBAxmbDRmxpcDM0pwszV1jUpWwTgNsMWwc%3D&h=21610f53\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Qooah.com</a> : <a href=\"https://qooah.com/2017/05/10/fuchsia-os-armadillo-preview/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fqooah.com%2F2017%2F05%2F10%2Ffuchsia-os-armadillo-preview%2F&d=PT6dGXJ5JuBAxmbDRmxpcDM0pwszV1jUpWwTgNsMWwc%3D&h=8886eace\" target=\"_blank\">https://qooah.com/2017/05/10/fuchsia-os-armadillo-preview/</a>"},{"pid":"5fa0b1e2212000fadf09bfa8301179b26d13ec9f","tid":237458,"uid":46389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T11:43:34.000Z","msg":"os用apk裝唔係flash rom?"},{"pid":"1958c6c929e56bae9871aec9f6a644e898c4f56f","tid":237458,"uid":37029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T11:49:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>os用apk裝唔係flash rom?</blockquote><br />\n佢呢個應該只係俾你試下個UI啫<br />\n好似Launcher咁<br />\n體驗版咋嘛"},{"pid":"9eb0a3b301d33381e5eb8c0a0bc334a07706ca5d","tid":237458,"uid":63846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T11:52:48.000Z","msg":"啲technique detail鳩寫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"812ba3fbb20f997055be82df188f1ad7ed5edc29","tid":237458,"uid":81345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T11:54:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>os用apk裝唔係flash rom?</blockquote><br />\n咁智障都問得出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b11676c0fd62a1ab046705be8a9642ab7f14a718","tid":237458,"uid":3488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T15:07:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>os用apk裝唔係flash rom?</blockquote><br />\n咁智障都問得出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc5fb6c3e70b9e53a9e5243a98e36206c241ba50","tid":237458,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T16:30:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1036b30134ef98058dc25b8cc02a82ce628e0ebe","tid":237458,"uid":99536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T03:22:59.000Z","msg":"一開始會唔會俾人hack到仆街？"},{"pid":"80212306f080583bb